# Question Protocol Rules

## Asking Questions
- Ask one question at a time
- Document in questions.md
- Include context and impact
- Note urgency if critical
- Wait for response before proceeding

## Question Format
- Clear and specific
- Include background
- State impact on implementation
- Note dependencies
- Suggest possible answers

## Handling Answers
- Document in questions.md
- Update implementation if needed
- Record in decisions.md if significant
- Update security documentation if relevant
- Proceed with next steps

## Blocking Questions
- Mark as blocking if critical
- Update task status
- Document impact on timeline
- Suggest alternatives if possible
- Wait for resolution 